OL,3,CPharmacy paying 'over the odds' to
OL,4,Csource medicines in short supply
OL,6,FITV Border's Katie Templeton-Knight
OL,7,Freports
OL,9,FA pharmacy has said it is struggling
OL,10,Fto provide customers with certain
OL,11,Fmedications due to a lack of supply.
OL,13,FA report carried out by Community
OL,14,FPharmacy England found that 79 per
OL,15,Fcent of those surveyed believe
OL,16,F"patient health is being put at risk
OL,17,Fdue to medicine supply issues."
OL,19,FSimon Butterworth's family have run
OL,20,FCollins & Butterworth Pharmacy in
OL,21,FHawkshead for almost 40 years.
