OL,3,CPharmacy paying 'over the odds' to
OL,4,Csource medicines in short supply
OL,6,FHe said: "First we've got to
OL,7,Fapologise, it's distressing to
OL,8,Fpatients, they've got to know when
OL,9,Fthey can get the medications they need.
OL,11,F"We're having to spend time hunting
OL,12,Ffor it, looking for it or doing our
OL,13,Fbest to find ways to solve that
OL,14,Fproblem for them.
OL,16,F"Certain items are actually costing
OL,17,Fmore to buy than we get paid for them
OL,18,Fby the NHS.
OL,20,F"The NHS has a fixed tariff, and we're
OL,21,Fhaving to pay more money.
