OL,3,CPharmacy paying 'over the odds' to
OL,4,Csource medicines in short supply
OL,6,F"An item we were trying to get this
OL,7,Fmorning was 250 per cent higher than
OL,8,Fthe tariff price, which is significant
OL,9,Fand builds up over lots of items.
OL,11,FThe National Pharmacy Agency reports
OL,12,Fthat around 10 pharmacies a week are
OL,13,Fclosing every week.
OL,15,FCommunity Pharmacy England has warned
OL,16,Fthat without intervention, these
OL,17,Fpressures will "lead to the closure of
OL,18,Fmore pharmacies".
