OL,6,FMubasher Ali, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FCommunity Pharmacy Lancashire and
OL,8,FSouth Cumbria said: "We need to make
OL,9,Fit more feasible for pharmacies.
OL,11,F"We've got to sort out this funding,
OL,12,Fit's absolutely crucial to us."
OL,14,FA spokesperson from the Department of
OL,15,FHealth said: "There are around 14,000
OL,16,Flicensed medicines and the
OL,17,Foverwhelming majority are in good
OL,18,Fsupply.
