OL,6,F"Supply issues can arise for a wide
OL,7,Frange of reasons and are not specific
OL,8,Fto the UK.
OL,10,F"Our priority is to mitigate risks
OL,11,Fposed by those issues and to help
OL,12,Fensure that patients continue to get
OL,13,Fthe treatments they need.
OL,15,F"Thankfully most issues can be managed
OL,16,Fwith minimal impact to patients.
